@node Specialist notation
@chapter Specialist notation

This chapter explains how to create musical notation for specific
types of instrument or in specific styles.

Orchestral and ensemble music is not addressed in a separate section;
however, several notions commonly useful in orchestral scores are
found in @ref{References for opera and stage musicals}.

